  "“Protocolized Openness” confirmed as an English-language paper (with Chinese parallel passages) — no separate translation planned.": "„Protocolized Openness” is bevestigd als Engelstalig paper (met parallelle Chinese passages) — er is geen aparte vertaling gepland.",
